like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T12:47:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>要受訓兩年，呢個部門好孤寒<br />\n真係有抱負同使命感先好入</blockquote><br />\n點孤寒法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解可以拖到train2年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2d6ed8a38045c028d2249b9373c69c0722a4469","tid":346680,"uid":12653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:24:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>要受訓兩年，呢個部門好孤寒<br />\n真係有抱負同使命感先好入</blockquote><br />\n點孤寒法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隊員就要受訓大半年，長官聽講就係兩年<br />\n做做下會有好多時候逼你返嚟，做嘢但唔簽更紙<br />\n不過如果你做到美沙酮診所果d就正<br />\n當正職返嘅話有20kup"},{"pid":"d839815bdaf319a7ba53bf12648b06c454e6019c","tid":346680,"uid":12653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:27:41.000Z","msg":"至於實務方面，真係on撚鳩<br />\n明明大家都係政府部門，啲em call就俾哂st.john做<br />\nAms啲車就擺多過用<br />\n<br />\n真係學到野嘅就只有單車隊同埋美沙酮診所"},{"pid":"d4b7f2d11b0c394280df279b1f2dfc18b1de2f71","tid":346680,"uid":65368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T14:27:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>至於實務方面，真係on撚鳩<br />\n明明大家都係政府部門，啲em call就俾哂st.john做<br />\nAms啲車就擺多過用<br />\n<br />\n真係學到野嘅就只有單車隊同埋美沙酮診所</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打做左好耐？"},{"pid":"8c704c5b072f102b3e5204f3123b00884148cc6f","tid":346680,"uid":6612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T14:31:26.000Z","msg":"做officer等於返多份無錢既正職 無時間抱負落到隊好快會走 亦都好多officer走"},{"pid":"2e45a3d94ae01c44a8dcaf4bf46113299ef2b49e","tid":346680,"uid":130298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T15:25:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>至於實務方面，真係on撚鳩<br />\n明明大家都係政府部門，啲em call就俾哂st.john做<br />\nAms啲車就擺多過用<br />\n<br />\n真係學到野嘅就只有單車隊同埋美沙酮診所</blockquote><br />\nSt.john一樣on9，兩隊都係西，你可以話ams係睇錢份上"},{"pid":"e61333eb3d7f54ee3369c3a87456aa7c56bdb34f","tid":346680,"uid":7832,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T16:09:26.000Z","msg":"更又少 屎又要你食 人又要你管<br />\n正正經經當興趣做散仔仲撚爽"},{"pid":"fc4bd9bc421fbabe264eda4b9c705b3f73eb5fbe","tid":346680,"uid":12653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T00:47:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>至於實務方面，真係on撚鳩<br />\n明明大家都係政府部門，啲em call就俾哂st.john做<br />\nAms啲車就擺多過用<br />\n<br />\n真係學到野嘅就只有單車隊同埋美沙酮診所</blockquote><br />\nSt.john一樣on9，兩隊都係西，你可以話ams係睇錢份上</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都知入呢d隊唔係為錢係想學野，你話賽馬果d俾st.john我無異議，始終都係英國佬野，益番自己友<br />\n<br />\n但真係搵唔到理由點解會俾咁多em call佢地做<br />\n真係大家一人一半都冇咁火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f9a737c3b3b1d75d70870f28203b4f1054a246c","tid":346680,"uid":12653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T00:49:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做officer等於返多份無錢既正職 無時間抱負落到隊好快會走 亦都好多officer走</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nOfficer做美沙酮診所好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ce9b430c864a5ddee7e2d8f00b06821e2adf122","tid":346680,"uid":12653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T00:49:38.000Z","msg":"同埋唔記得講，ams係三個月先出一次糧"},{"pid":"b30da3b813dd04d1a1b1ccf3be6a04e7e222b9ec","tid":346680,"uid":7832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T13:25:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>至於實務方面，真係on撚鳩<br />\n明明大家都係政府部門，啲em call就俾哂st.john做<br />\nAms啲車就擺多過用<br />\n<br />\n真係學到野嘅就只有單車隊同埋美沙酮診所</blockquote><br />\nSt.john一樣on9，兩隊都係西，你可以話ams係睇錢份上</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都知入呢d隊唔係為錢係想學野，你話賽馬果d俾st.john我無異議，始終都係英國佬野，益番自己友<br />\n<br />\n但真係搵唔到理由點解會俾咁多em call佢地做<br />\n真係大家一人一半都冇咁火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></bl